data.description: Look at the end of this description for all these updates for this house!! Large home, spacious and updated! This home is right in the middle of town. Close to Hwy 231, big corner lot and was renovated in 2021. Large living room when you walk in the front door and the kitchen is wide open. There is vinyl plank floor, new cabinets and room for lots of furniture. The main bedroom is off on one side of the home with a large closet and there is a laundry room/ office as well. Electrical, plumbing, HVAC, roof and windows were all updated in 2021. There is an extra large septic tank so there is no sewage bill. This house is a must see! Schedule your showing today!!Info from seller:Water bill is generally $28/monthTrash is affordable too!Roof redone in 2021Commercial size septic tank pumped August 2021Rockwool insulation water repellent, fire retardant put in attic Nov 2021New heating and cooling vents 2022New detached garage 2022Electrician ran new wires 2022Pond cleaned/ pump and filter 2022Wood replaced on deck 2021Gutters 2023New condensation pump 2023 for the houseHeating and cooling cleaned 2023New septic pump 2021This is just some of the things they have done to updated the house since they purchased it. Come in and check it out!! Schedule a showing today.
